  <h1>GST Late Fee <span class="grad-text">Chart FY 2026-27</span></h1>
  <p class="answer-first"><b>GST late fee under Section 47 is Rs.50 per day (Rs.20 for nil) for GSTR-1 and GSTR-3B, and Rs.200 per day for GSTR-9, each subject to turnover-based caps.</b> Rates are combined CGST + SGST; there is no IGST late fee.</p>
