    <div class="faq"><h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>
      <details><summary>What is the GST late fee per day?</summary><p>Rs.50 per day (Rs.25 CGST + Rs.25 SGST) for GSTR-1/3B with tax, and Rs.20 per day for nil returns, subject to a turnover-based maximum cap.</p></details>
      <details><summary>Is there a late fee under IGST?</summary><p>No. Late fee under Section 47 is levied only under the CGST Act and the respective SGST/UTGST Act.</p></details>
      <details><summary>How is the GST late fee capped?</summary><p>By annual turnover under Notification 07/2023-Central Tax; nil returns are capped at Rs.500 and others between Rs.2,000 and Rs.10,000 depending on turnover.</p></details>
